{"id": 2494, "genre": 1001, "title": "【好奇心x轩尼诗V.S.O.P】现如今，什么最能让你感受到生活的愉悦？", "description": "保持初心，才能大步前行。", "record_count": 11563, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20181224163110zoxOQ8Mw67rPe1lm.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 3, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-12-25T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 318725, "content": "和世界融为一体", "image": null, "praise_count": 52, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1500262}, {"id": 318726, "content": "开车到家停车休息的几分钟", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540903}, {"id": 318727, "content": "暴瘦 暴富", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540930}, {"id": 318728, "content": "随心所欲", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1478375}, {"id": 319240, "content": "周末不用加班", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1484388}, {"id": 318729, "content": "活出真正的自己，有某几项爱好并坚持下去", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540935}, {"id": 318730, "content": "一人一狗一世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1473177}, {"id": 320266, "content": "喜欢的人也喜欢自己并且最重要的是学习变好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1546411}, {"id": 318731, "content": "有需求的时候，有爱做", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 711174}, {"id": 337932, "content": "沙雕吧\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1631103}, {"id": 318732, "content": "思考", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 798057}, {"id": 319500, "content": "家里买了唱片机和黑胶唱片 每天盼着回家立刻用", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1427726}, {"id": 318733, "content": "何以解忧，唯有暴富！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540957}, {"id": 318734, "content": "发现异地恋其实并不可怕，等着远方的你，韩雨⁽˙³˙⁾◟(๑•́ ₃ •̀๑)◞⁽˙³˙⁾", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540960}, {"id": 318735, "content": "在合适的时间和对的人做喜欢的事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531372}, {"id": 318736, "content": "吃德芙巧克力，非带缠绕的瞬间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540969}, {"id": 318738, "content": "弹吉他🎸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1538312}, {"id": 318739, "content": "夜晚的独处", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1540966}, {"id": 318996, "content": "天还大亮，乘着晚霞就可以下班，买点菜自己做一顿晚餐。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162161}, {"id": 318741, "content": "肥宅快乐水~", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147717}, {"id": 318997, "content": "您的余额为：xxxxx+", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 939196}, {"id": 320277, "content": "遇一人白首，择一城终老。情不知所起，一往而深。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1517964}, {"id": 318742, "content": "躺到床上可以安心睡个觉的那一瞬间", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1319787}, {"id": 318999, "content": "在寒冬下找到工作", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1541963}, {"id": 319256, "content": "中彩票几亿不用工作环游世界", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 966090}, {"id": 318745, "content": "熬夜", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 460474}, {"id": 318746, "content": "晚上吃完安眠药后的拿两个小时，吃过的人应该都懂那种特殊的愉悦感", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 167801}, {"id": 319002, "content": "钱 不然还有什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1541979}, {"id": 319514, "content": "打球投篮很准的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1459976}, {"id": 321562, "content": "外面下雨，家里暖气短袖奶茶王者荣耀语音开黑，哦对，点了蜡烛开了香薰加湿器", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1552509}, {"id": 318747, "content": "感受到自己存在的价值", "image": null, "praise_count": 53, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1534810}, {"id": 318748, "content": "还清债务。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1513949}, {"id": 319004, "content": "早睡早起", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1541978}, {"id": 318749, "content": "一个安静的待在大学宿舍的厕所，抽着烟", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1416349}, {"id": 318750, "content": "被人喜欢，被认可！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 676110}, {"id": 318751, "content": "遇到一个我喜欢，同时也喜欢我的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1391939}, {"id": 318752, "content": "打最喜欢的游戏公司出品的游戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289571}, {"id": 318753, "content": "吃着肉，喝着可乐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1541010}, {"id": 318754, "content": "不用复习，就可以考试得高分😬😬😬😬", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1528022}, {"id": 319010, "content": "进入心心念念的公司", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1542002}, {"id": 318755, "content": "和喜欢的人聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1541017}, {"id": 319011, "content": "拍到喜欢的照片", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1541996}, {"id": 318756, "content": "不焦虑，和家人在一起", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1541021}, {"id": 319268, "content": "按时放假", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1543032}, {"id": 318757, "content": "既然标题都这么写了 那肯定是在周末夜晚与三五好友一齐畅饮“轩尼诗”之时 人生最为曼妙", "image": null, "praise_count": 45, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1491127}, {"id": 318758, "content": "有足够的时间躺着放空", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1355256}, {"id": 320038, "content": "每次放学后，一个人待在教室里，看着同学一个一个出校门，那时候感觉特别轻松而且很愉快，一点孤独的感觉也没有。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1449065}, {"id": 318759, "content": "每天下班看见老公的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 217198}, {"id": 318760, "content": "肆意地看小说。不再担心学习成绩和综测", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1541031}, {"id": 318762, "content": "想花钱不用考虑银行卡余额，不担心养老。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1535257}]}